'''Comedy music''' is [[music]] that is [[Comedy|comic]] or [[humor]]ous in nature, encompassing a wide variety of [[music genre]]s. Popular types of comedy music include [[parody music]], [[novelty song]]s, [[comedy rock]] and [[comedy hip hop]].

