The '''Military World Games''' is a [[multi-sport event]] for [[military sports]]people, organized by the [[International Military Sports Council]] (CISM). The Games have been held since 1995, although championships for separate sports had been held for some years. A winter edition of the games has been recently created, the [[2010 Winter Military World Games|first edition]] was organized by the [[Italy|Italian]] [[regione|region]] of [[Aosta Valley]] from 20 to 25 of March 2010.<ref>{{cite web |title=Guidance for Submitting a Candidature to the Organization of the 1st CISM Winter Military Games |url=http://www.cismmilsport.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/guide-MilitaryWinterGames.pdf |work=[[International Military Sports Council|CISM official website]] |publisher=CISM Winter Military Games Bidding Book |date= |accessdate= }}</ref>

